<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id0db6ae51-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795" identifier="/us/usc/t20/s2003"><num value="2003">§ 2003.</num><heading> Other Federal memorials prohibited</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Harry S Truman Scholarship Program as authorized by this chapter shall be the sole Federal memorial to President Harry S Truman.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id0db6ae52-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795">(<ref href="/us/pl/93/642/s4">Pub. L. 93–642, § 4</ref>, <date date="1975-01-04">Jan. 4, 1975</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/88/2277">88 Stat. 2277</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
